title: Cheerful Chicago Holiday Cards
description:
The artist of this design, Lynette Velazquez says "My dream is to use emotion to create artwork that has a lasting effect on its viewers.". These unique holiday cards were created by a student employed in the Marwen Foundation career development programs. Marwen is an after-school arts organization that provides high-quality visual arts, college planning, and career development programs--all free of charge--to Chicago's under-served young people.

Interior greeting reads "May your holidays be bright!"
Set of 12 cards with envelopes

5 in. x 7 in.
